Use the standard library
This is how to tri of n:
  Remember that out is [1, 3]
  When n is at most 2, then:
    The answer is out
  End when
  Remember that i is 3
  Do this diff of n and 2 times:
    When remainder of i and 2 is 1, then:
      Add out to quotient of sum of i and 1 and 2
    But, if not:
      Add out to product of i and i
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is out
